apoc.couchbase.document

Class CouchbaseQueryResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • apoc.couchbase.document.CouchbaseQueryResult

  • public class CouchbaseQueryResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Transports the list of JsonObjects retrieved by a N1QL query so that it can be Stream-ed and returned by the procedures

    Every JsonObjects retrieved by a N1QL query is first converted into a Map<String, Object> and then added to the embedded queryResult list.

    Since:
    15.8.2016
    See Also:
    CouchbaseUtils.convertToCouchbaseQueryResult(List), N1qlQueryResult
